stories.title: Lack of ammo stymies Bangladesh
stories.subTitle: Bangladesh v India, 1st ODI, Chittagong
stories.summary: When you hear cricketers and former cricketers repeat, ad nauseum, that cricket is a funny game, and that anything can happen in a one-day international, you wonder if they're watching the same game
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Anand Vasu in Chittagong
